      <div class="biz-card"><h3>🏋️ Gyms &amp; Spas</h3><p>Towel service machines. Member amenity, broken equipment affects the member experience and retention immediately.</p></div>
      <div class="biz-card"><h3>🏥 Care Facilities</h3><p>Assisted living, nursing homes, and care facilities with high-volume on-premises laundry. Service window scheduling important.</p></div>
      <div class="biz-card"><h3>🏢 Multi-Building Portfolios</h3><p>Property management companies with multiple buildings across SoCal, LA, OC, Ventura, IE. Priority service agreements available. One call covers all your properties.</p></div>
    </div>

    <!-- PROPERTY MANAGER BLOCK -->
    <div class="pm-block">
      <div class="pm-label">🏠 For SoCal Property Managers</div>
      <h3>The information you need when calling about a laundry room repair</h3>
      <p>Property managers managing multiple buildings across SoCal need a reliable commercial laundry repair partner that understands building access challenges, parking restrictions, gated entries, elevator windows, and laundry room lockboxes. When you call us, have this information ready and we'll route the visit efficiently.</p>

      <div class="pm-grid">
        <div class="pm-item"><strong>Building address</strong><span>Full address including unit or floor if laundry room is in a specific location</span></div>
        <div class="pm-item"><strong>Access details</strong><span>Parking instructions, gate code, elevator rules, and who meets the tech on-site</span></div>
